metadata.title: FitFusion Rebranding Kickoff & Planning

Discussions covered timelines (3 weeks for design, legal review by August 7, 2025), brand messaging, and trademark considerations. Initial concepts are due July 16, 2025, with brand voice guidelines ready for review by June 26, 2025.
